name: TheDailyOrange
0:
”Alexa, open the daily orange”
”Alexa, ask the daily orange what's in the news”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: the daily orange
des: Use this skill to hear the headlines from "The Daily Orange - Syracuse University's Student Run Newspaper" RSS feed. All you need to do is say "Open the Daily Orange", then ask Alexa to "tell me the headlines". Hope you enjoy!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
